
*** TRON PROJECTS ***

This document lists all projects inside the tron repository.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> comy - libtron_comy.so 		

depends:
- libtron_tuly
- log4cxx

* Library for inter process communication.
* Should be extended with ZeroMQ library.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> maty - libtron_maty.so 		

* Library for mathematical utilities.


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> nety - libtron_nety.so 		

depends:
- libtron_comy
- libtron_talky
- libtron_tuly
- log4cxx

* Library for communication nodes. 
* Nodes working with talky language, comy communication and message queues.


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> talky - libtron_talky.so		

depends:
- log4cxx

* Defines a standard language for communication between robotic control processes. 
* Language divided in topics, categories and concepts.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> tivy - libtron_tivy.so		

depends:
- opencv_core
- opencv_highgui

* Library for gui development based in OpenCV: cartesian charts, historical charts ...


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> tuly - libtron_tuly.so 		

* Library for utilities: string handling, file handling, thread management, brooks control classes ...


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> tron_test - tron_test 		

depends:
- libtron_comy
- libtron_maty
- libtron_nety
- libtron_talky
- libtron_tivy
- libtron_tuly
- log4cxx

* Test program used for showing and testing tron functionalities. Each lib has its own class with sample code.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


